<p>The Platinum Triangle area, Anaheim's newest urban development, offers excellent opportunities for integrated solar and HVAC design in modern construction. East Anaheim's diverse housing stock, ranging from mid-century ranch homes to newer developments, presents varied solar installation scenarios, with older homes often benefiting most from combined solar and HVAC upgrades due to aging, inefficient systems. Each neighborhood's specific utility infrastructure and HOA regulations can impact installation timelines and equipment choices, making local expertise crucial for optimal system design.</p>

